{
  "stem": "24171.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's not that the smoke came in, it was kind of that-- that feeling, that bone burning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was terrible, terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beaten.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I was beaten myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, because-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] twice I was beaten.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first time I was beaten, there was a men's barrack, and-- and it had, kind of, like a fence.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "An iron fence and a gate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think it was electricity, and it, it's not that kind of a fence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some-- I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was no electricity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was always a guy staying by the gate when they were home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know where they were working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe they were for Schindler, working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We don't know or what, because we never heard of that name there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or maybe if we heard, we didn't pay attention.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they had water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They worked kind of like-- they had, I think, a better kitchen, or better food or whatever, because they were-- really looked kind of like well-fed people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were in civilian dress, like-- like boots, with kind of like almost like the Germans-- surrounded all those pants, like horseback riding.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, that stuff.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they had water there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then we found out that when they're not there, and nobody stays by the gate, and the gate is open, and we could go in to that place where they have water, that's kind of like by the men's room.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember if it was by a men's room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But there was a lot of them there, kind of like sinks.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
